@startuml
title ATM Control - Polished Requirement Specification for Scenario 7

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state WaitingForPIN
state ValidatingPIN
state WaitingForCustomerChoice
state ProcessingRequest

state Ejecting
state Confiscating
state Terminating
state ClosedDown

Idle --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Third Invalid PIN, Card Stolen, Card Expired / Confiscate, Update Status
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForCustomerChoice : Valid PIN / Display Menu

WaitingForPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
ValidatingPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
WaitingForCustomerChoice --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject

WaitingForCustomerChoice --> ProcessingRequest : Request Selected / Process Request, Display Wait

ProcessingRequest --> Terminating : Request Approved / Process Request, Update Status
ProcessingRequest --> Confiscating : Card Stolen, Card Expired / Confiscate, Update Status

Terminating --> Idle : After (Elapsed Time) [Closedown Not Requested]

Confiscating --> Terminating : Card Confiscated / Display Confiscated

ClosedDown --> Idle : System Down / Display System Down

@enduml
